subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: Venus Williams dominated Vera Zvonareva, 6-2, 6-2, to give Team Americas the victory over Russia in the Hong Kong team tournament. Williams finished her only warm-up event before the Australian Open without dropping a set in singles play.
